I resent the implication—

132
00:04:07,637 --> 00:04:08,768
- Hello?

133
00:04:08,812 --> 00:04:09,943
- Okay, I'm up to something,
Terrence.

134
00:04:09,987 --> 00:04:11,249
- Hello?

135
00:04:11,292 --> 00:04:12,206
- I messed with Holt and
Kevin's shared calendar.

136
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:14,469
