Is everything okay?

145
00:04:36,013 --> 00:04:37,144
- No.

146
00:04:37,188 --> 00:04:38,755
We just had a knock-down,
drag-out fight.

147
00:04:38,798 --> 00:04:40,670
My calendar had
the Lake House as free.

148
00:04:40,713 --> 00:04:42,976
- Strange.
Mine had it as unoccupied.

149
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:45,326
- Well, it seems
we're at an impasse.

150
00:04:45,370 --> 00:04:47,502
- I would call it
more of a deadlock.

151
