is about to enter the room.

159
00:05:00,646 --> 00:05:03,344
Raymond Holt
entering the kitchen!

160
00:05:03,388 --> 00:05:05,172
- Jake, this is bad.

161
00:05:05,216 --> 00:05:07,479
- Raymond Holt entering
the second sitting room.

162
00:05:07,522 --> 00:05:08,872
