206
00:06:25,339 --> 00:06:26,384
- How long have you been there?

207
00:06:26,427 --> 00:06:28,473
- Oh, man, I have no idea.

208
00:06:29,604 --> 00:06:30,997
- Hey, were you followed?
- Nope.

